F.Intrinsic.String.Build("select ORDER_NO as SO,NAME_CUSTOMER as Customer,LEFT(RECORD_NO,3) as Line, PART as Part,description as Description, QTY_BO AS Qty, PRICE as Price, COST as Cost, CASE PRICE WHEN 0 THEN 0 ELSE 100*(1-(COST/PRICE)) END as Margin,case DATE_ITEM_PROM when '1900-01-01' then '2099-01-01' else DATE_ITEM_PROM end as DueDate, (QTY_BO*PRICE) AS Extension from V_ORDER_LINES,V_CUSTOMER_MASTER where V_ORDER_LINES.CUSTOMER=V_CUSTOMER_MASTER.CUSTOMER and ORDER_NO='{0}'",V.DataTable.dtPrjO(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,V.Local.sSql)

F.Intrinsic.String.Build("select ORDER_NO as SO, NAME_CUSTOMER as Customer,LEFT(ORDER_REC,3) AS Line, PART as Part,order_desc as Description, QTY_SHIPPED AS Qty, PRICE as Price,COST as Cost,MARGIN as Margin, DATE_SHIP as ShipDate, EXTENSION as Extension from V_SHIPMENT_LINES, V_CUSTOMER_MASTER where V_SHIPMENT_LINES.CUSTOMER=V_CUSTOMER_MASTER.CUSTOMER and ORDER_NO='{0}'",V.DataTable.dtPrjO(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,V.Local.sSql)

F.Intrinsic.String.Build("select ORDER_NO as SO,NAME_CUSTOMER as Customer,LEFT(ORDER_LINE,3) AS Line,PART as Part,description as Description, QTY_SHIPPED AS Qty, PRICE as Price, COST as Cost, MARGIN as Margin, DATE_INVOICE as InvoiceDate, INVOICE as Invoice,EXTENSION as Extension from V_ORDER_HIST_LINE,V_CUSTOMER_MASTER where V_ORDER_HIST_LINE.CUSTOMER=V_CUSTOMER_MASTER.CUSTOMER and ORDER_NO='{0}'",V.DataTable.dtPrjO(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,V.Local.sSql)

F.Intrinsic.String.Build("select QUOTE_NO as Quote,NAME_CUSTOMER as Customer,LEFT(RECORD_NO,3) AS Line,PART as Part,description as Description,QTY_QUOTED AS Qty, PRICE as Price, COST as Cost, CASE PRICE WHEN 0 THEN 0 ELSE (1-(COST/PRICE)) END as Margin, DATE_ITEM_PROM as DueDate, EXTENSION as Extension from V_QUOTE_LINES, V_QUOTE_BILL_TO where V_QUOTE_LINES.QUOTE_NO=V_QUOTE_BILL_TO.QUOTE_NO AND QUOTE_NO='{0}'",V.DataTable.dtPrjQ(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,V.Local.sSql)

F.Intrinsic.String.Concat("Select Part, Cost, Qty_Order From V_PO_HISTORY Where Purchase_Order='",V.DataTable.dtPrjP(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,"' And PO_LINE='",V.DataTable.dtPrjP(V.Local.iC).VALUE2!FieldValTrim,"0' And Date_Received='1900-01-01'",V.Local.sSqlPO)

V.Local.sSql.Set("select PURCHASE_ORDER as PO,NAME_VENDOR as Vendor,LEFT(PO_LINE,3) AS Line, PART as Part, description as Description, QTY_ORDER as Qty, sum(qty_received+QTY_RECD_NOT_INSP) AS QtyRec,COST as Cost,DATE_DUE as DueDate, QTY_ORDER*COST AS Extension, sum(qty_received+QTY_RECD_NOT_INSP)*COST AS ExtRec from v_po_history, V_Vendor_MASTER where V_PO_HISTORY.VENDOR=V_VENDOR_MASTER.VENDOR")

F.Intrinsic.String.Concat(V.Local.sSql," AND purchase_order='",V.DataTable.dtPrjP(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,"' AND PO_LINE='",V.DataTable.dtPrjP(V.Local.iC).VALUE2!FieldValTrim,"0'"," AND PART='",V.DataTable.dtPOList(V.Local.iC2).Part!FieldValTrim,"' AND COST='",V.DataTable.dtPOList(V.Local.iC2).Cost!FieldVal,"' AND QTY_ORDER='",V.DataTable.dtPOList(V.Local.iC2).Qty_Order!FieldVal,"' group by PURCHASE_ORDER,NAME_VENDOR,PART,LINE,QTY_ORDER,COST,EXTENSION,DATE_DUE,description",V.Local.sSql)

F.Intrinsic.String.Build("select JOB as Job, SUFFIX as Suffix, PART as Part, DESCRIPTION as Description, DATE_DUE as DueDate, DATE_CLOSED as ClosedDate, (QTY_ORDER-QTY_COMPLETED) as Qty, AMT_MATERIAL as Material, AMT_LABOR as Labor, AMT_OVERHEAD as Overhead, case DATE_CLOSED when '1900-01-01' then 'Open' else 'Closed' end as Status from V_JOB_HEADER Where JOB='{0}' and suffix = '{1}'",V.DataTable.dtPrjJ(V.Local.iC).VALUE!FieldValTrim,V.DataTable.dtPrjJ(V.Local.iC).VALUE2!FieldValTrim,V.Local.sSql)
